backlog.description: Validate survey weights and replicate design metadata against data files.
Produce exploratory weighted summaries for key wellbeing and socioeconomic outcomes.
Request official survey design weights or documentation from data provider.
Analyze missingness drivers for self-love and abuse items; plan imputation strategy.
Prototype multiple imputation workflow for self-love and abuse items (seed 20251016).
Review imputed vs complete-case summaries and design robustness checks.
Design MI reduced-auxiliary sensitivity run and document command template.
Execute reduced-auxiliary MI sensitivity run and compare against prototype outputs.
Synthesize reduced-auxiliary MI diagnostics into PAP robustness text and manifest notes.

next_actions.description: Coordinate sending of survey weight request; track provider response.

notes: Reduced-auxiliary diagnostics documented in PAP and manifest notes; awaiting official survey weight metadata before PAP freeze.
regeneration_command: python analysis/code/eda_weighted_summaries.py && python analysis/code/missingness_analysis.py && python analysis/code/mice_prototype.py --dataset childhoodbalancedpublic_original.csv --config config/agent_config.yaml --seed 20251016 --n-imputations 20 --burn-in 10 && python analysis/code/review_imputed_vs_complete.py --dataset childhoodbalancedpublic_original.csv --imputed data/derived/childhoodbalancedpublic_mi_prototype.csv.gz --mapping analysis/imputation/mice_variable_map.json --csv-out tables/imputed_vs_complete_summary.csv --md-out analysis/imputation/imputed_vs_complete_summary.md --seed 20251016 && python analysis/code/mice_prototype.py --dataset childhoodbalancedpublic_original.csv --config config/agent_config.yaml --seed 20251016 --n-imputations 20 --burn-in 10 --run-label reduced_aux --columns selfage biomale gendermale cis education classchild classteen classcurrent networth 'I love myself (2l8994l)' 'during ages *0-12*: your parents verbally or emotionally abused you (mds78zu)' && python analysis/code/review_imputed_vs_complete.py --dataset childhoodbalancedpublic_original.csv --imputed data/derived/childhoodbalancedpublic_mi_reduced_aux.csv.gz --mapping analysis/imputation/mice_variable_map__reduced_aux.json --csv-out tables/imputed_vs_complete_summary__reduced_aux.csv --md-out analysis/imputation/imputed_vs_complete_summary__reduced_aux.md --seed 20251016 && python analysis/code/compare_imputation_runs.py --summary-a analysis/imputation/mice_imputation_summary.csv --summary-b analysis/imputation/mice_imputation_summary__reduced_aux.csv --label-a prototype --label-b reduced_aux --csv-out tables/imputation_run_comparison__prototype_vs_reduced_aux.csv --md-out analysis/imputation/imputation_run_comparison__prototype_vs_reduced_aux.md --seed 20251016
